name: Lost Highway Phaser
details:
PhaserAnalogue circuit
Switchable slow / fast speed with independent rate and depth
Switchable sine and triangle waveform
Controls: Rate 1, Depth 1, Rate 2, Depth 2, Bend, Feedback, Sens
Switch: 2 Mini toggles for 4-8 stage phasing and sine or triangle waveform
Foot switch: Bypass and slow / fast
True bypass
6.3 mm jack input
6.3 mm jack output
AC adapter connector: Hollow plug socket 5.5 x 2.1 mm, negative pole inside
